Expansion XMPP4R to authenticate with Facebook Connect in Ruby

======================================
Install:
======================================
gem install xmpp4r_facebook

======================================
Sample code:
======================================
require 'xmpp4r_facebook'

id = '<sender username>@chat.facebook.com'
to = '-<user id>chat.facebook.com'
body = "hello, Im not spam!"
subject = 'message from ruby'
message = Jabber::Message.new to, body
message.subject = subject

client = Jabber::Client.new Jabber::JID.new(id)
client.connect
client.auth_sasl(Jabber::SASL::XFacebookPlatform.new(client, '<api key>', '<access token>', '<app secret>'), nil)
client.send message
client.close



